text: Gräfendorf is a community in Main-Spessart in the Regierungsbezirk of Lower Franconia (Unterfranken) in Bavaria, Germany and a member of the Verwaltungsgemeinschaft (Administrative Community) of Gemünden am Main. ==Geography== ===Location=== Gräfendorf is in the Würzburg Region near Gemünden am Main. ===Constituent communities=== The community has the following Gemarkungen (traditional rural cadastral areas) and Ortsteile: Gräfendorf, Michelau an der Saale, Schonderfeld, Weickersgrüben, Wolfsmünster. ==References== Category:Main-Spessart
title: Gräfendorf
